        <num>47-11-40</num>
        <content>
          <p>Before any person shall be eligible to participate in the fund he or she must:</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1958, p. 185, § 7; Ga. L. 1959, p. 354, § 1; Ga. L. 1961, p. 57, §§ 1, 2; Ga. L. 1968, p. 548, §§ 3-5; Ga. L. 1976, p. 754, § 2; Ga. L. 1979, p. 596, § 2; Ga. L. 1982, p. 3, § 47; Ga. L. 1990, p. 543, § 2; Ga. L. 1991, p. 130, § 1; Ga. L. 1992, p. 1037, § 2; Ga. L. 1994, p. 342, § 1; Ga. L. 1998, p. 166, §§ 1, 2; Ga. L. 2000, p. 1278, § 1; Ga. L. 2010, p. 1207, § 66/SB 436; Ga. L. 2016, p. 354, § 1/HB 635.)</p>
          <p>The 2010 amendment,
      effective July 1, 2010, substituted "board of commissioners" for "board of trustees" three times in this Code section.</p>
          <p>The 2016 amendment,
      effective July 1, 2016, substituted "30 years" for "20 years" at the end of paragraph (7).</p>
